Key Match Events: Hakim Ziyech scored in the first half as Morocco beat Zambia 1-0.
Morocco’s stand-in captain left the pitch with an ankle injury at half-time.
Ivory Coast secured a place in the last-16 as one of the best third-place finishers.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Ivory Coast sneaked into the last-16, sparking celebrations in the Laurent Pokou Stadium.
The game had very few chances for the 12,847 crowd at the Amadou Gon Coulibaly Stadium.
